title: Dark Season 1 (2017)Netflix
description:
This is the complete first season of Dark from Netflix. It is a German Language program, with external English subtitles provided in SRT format. It was released and encoded in XVID format by AFG...but episode 6 was released with an English dub instead of the original German audio track, so I stripped the dubbed track and replaced it with the proper original german audio track, extracted from the Strife mkv. The audio was converted from AC3 to MP3 as to keep it consistent with other AFG releases. I also had to create the srt for episode 10, as noone else had done that yet. So here it is, in all it's full, german spoken, english subtitled glory for your enjoyment and viewing pleasure. 

PLEASE SEED!!! Thanks, aNaRCHo
